                "invention-title": [
                    "System and method for manufacturing iron through hydrogen electricity reduction of iron ore",
                    "一种铁矿石氢电还原制铁的系统及方法"
                ]
            },
            "abstract": [
                {
                    "p": "The invention belongs to the field of energy and metallurgy. Specifically, the invention discloses a system and a method for producing iron by hydrogen electricity reduction of iron ore. The iron ore concentrate is reduced into low-valence iron oxide through fluidized hydrogen reduction, the acidolysis efficiency is improved, and low-acid conversion is achieved. And through high-temperature desulfurization, resource utilization and sulfur element circulation of acidolysis residues and purification residues are realized. Sulfur dioxide is introduced into an acidolysis filtration process, and the acidolysis process is enhanced by using the reducibility of sulfur dioxide. Ferrous sulfate solution valence state control, pure iron preparation, sulfuric acid regeneration and oxygen and hydrogen recycling are achieved through electroreduction iron production. A high-temperature medium is generated through the solar furnace, heat is supplied to the fluidized hydrogen reduction and high-temperature desulfurization procedures, and low carbonization of energy is achieved. The method is suitable for large-scale continuous hydrogen electroreduction iron production of iron ore, and has the advantages of high efficiency, low energy consumption, no pollution, ultralow emission of carbon dioxide and the like."
                },
                {
                    "p": "本发明属于能源、冶金领域。具体地，本发明公开了一种铁矿石氢电还原制铁的系统及方法。通过流态化氢气还原将铁精矿还原为低价铁氧化物，提高酸解效率，实现低酸转化。通过高温脱硫，实现酸解渣和净化渣的资源化利用和硫元素循环。通过将二氧化硫通入酸解过滤工序，利用二氧化硫的还原性强化酸解过程。通过电还原制铁实现硫酸亚铁溶液价态控制、纯铁制备、硫酸再生、氧气和氢气回收利用。通过太阳能炉产生高温介质，为流态化氢气还原和高温脱硫工序供热，实现能源低碳化。本发明适用于铁矿石大规模、连续化氢电还原制铁，具有效率高、能耗低、无污染和二氧化碳超低排放等优点。"
                }
            ]
